<L>__{interior swann's mansion study day}
<A>__{venetian blinds shut out most of the sunlight, but a lamp burns on the desk (huge), showing us the furniture (leather), the books (innumerable), and the figure of swann, sitting behind the desk smoking a cigar. he's lost some hair and some colour over the years, but he still has the same hypnotic eyes. he studies the l.a. times in front of him.}
<B>__{on the open page}
<A>__{"fortune teller brutally murdered," the headline announces. underneath, a photograph of quaid's wrecked room. we close in on the photograph, and catch a glimpse of harry, standing looking at the chaos. camera. moves down to the text beneath, and on to the name "harry d'amour." on swann, pensive as he studies the paper.}
